
PLEASE NOTE: The current version of ROLLING RONNY is a demonstration
             version only. The level designs are not yet completed.
             Only two (of the five planned) levels are ready to run in
             this demo-version. The errands in this version (see "how
             to play ROLLING RONNY) are just simple test-and-try samples.
             We are still working on more sophisticated and tricky 
             errands and jobs for Ronny. Only very few sound effects
             could be implemented up to now. The difficulty level
             has still to be corrected and adapted for the final version.
             We are positive about finishing the game until Christmas 1990
             or early (January/February) next year. But we are sure that
             this game is going to be addictive and great fun to play!
             
                                                The TOUCH of MAGIC team.



